dct_description_sm: Petroleum Economist Ltd. Deutsche Bank Relief shown by gradient tints. Depths shown by gradient tints.On upper left corner: Petroleum Economist Cartographic, energy maps.Tables showing reserves by publicly traded company and estimated reserves by NOC; world refineries capacities by country; gas statistics. Charts showing world reserves.
